== 开发和制作 ==
早在2009年11月[[Showtime电视网|Showtime电视网]]就打算根据[[史蒂芬·金|史蒂芬·金]]刚刚出版的小说开发同名科幻剧集《Under the Dome》，并请[[史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格|史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格]]和史蒂芬·金参与开发<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118011629?refCatId=1236|title=Spielberg, King team on 'Dome'|work=Variety|last=Littleton|first=Cynthia|date=November 19, 2009|accessdate=December 18, 2012|archive-date=2013-02-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EEsajtCn?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118011629/?refCatId=1236|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然而直到2011年8月Showtime电视网才正式开发该剧<ref>[http://www.deadline.com/2011/08/showtime-teams-with-steven-spielberg-and-stephen-king-for-under-the-dome-series/ Showtime Teams With Steven Spielberg And Stephen King For ‘Under The Dome’ Series]</ref><ref>[http://tvfantasy.net/2011/08/31/heterogeneous-range-the-lies-of-the-girl-greys-anatomy-nikita-bones-bags-ignorant-girl-criminal-psychology-and-other/ 异种区间、美少女的谎言、实习医生格蕾、尼基塔、尸骨袋、懵懂少女、犯罪心理及其他]</ref>，随后Showtime电视网让为《[[迷失|迷失]]》撰写过剧本的{{link-en|布赖恩·沃恩|Brian K. Vaughan}}来担撰写剧本<ref>[http://tvfantasy.net/2011/11/08/glee-gave-birth-to-hope-paradise-law-enforcement-miami-lawyers-big-as-cracks-suburbs-stories-and-other/ 欢乐合唱团、孕育希望、天堂执法者、迈阿密、小律师有大作为、裂痕、郊区故事及其他]</ref><ref>[http://www.deadline.com/2011/11/brian-k-vaughan-to-adapt-stephen-kings-under-the-dome-as-series-for-showtime/ Brian K. Vaughan To Adapt Stephen King’s ‘Under The Dome’ As Series For Showtime]</ref>。

在时隔一年后于2012年11月29日[[哥伦比亚广播公司|哥伦比亚广播公司]]（CBS）宣布预定该剧13集，将在2013年夏季播出<ref>[http://thefutoncritic.com/news/2012/11/29/cbs-will-take-viewers-under-the-dome-in-summer-2013-network-orders-13-episode-series-based-on-stephen-kings-best-selling-novel-814213/20121129cbs03/ CBS Will Take Viewers "Under the Dome" in Summer 2013 - Network Orders 13-Episode Series Based on Stephen King's Best-Selling Novel]</ref>；这次的突然变动是因为安培林娱乐意识到Showtime电视网对该剧不感兴趣而要求解约，于是Showtime电视网将该剧转交给同公司的广播网[[哥伦比亚广播公司|哥伦比亚广播公司]]来开发<ref>[http://tvfantasy.net/2012/11/30/cbs-orders-under-the-dome-by-stephne-king/ 快讯：“史蒂芬和史蒂文”双拳出击，科幻剧《穹顶之下》获直接预订]</ref>；在2013年的[[电视评论家协会|电视评论家协会冬季媒体见面会]]上CBS表示该剧第一季将相对独立，就算没有第二季也不会影响什么<ref>[http://tvfantasy.net/2013/01/13/newsletter-2013-01-13-tca-winter-cbs-showtime/ 1月13日简讯：电视评论协会冬季媒体见面会专题报道（Showtime、CBS）]</ref>；另外本剧不会采用小说的结局，这一点得到小说作者史蒂芬·金的 认可<ref>[http://tvfantasy.net/2013/06/24/under-the-dome-1x01-series-premiere/ 星期一：穹顶之下 S01E01 (新剧)(特稿)]</ref>。

该片于2013年2月28日开拍，主要在[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]][[威尔明顿_(北卡罗来纳州)|威尔明顿]]和绍斯波特拍摄<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://wilmonfilm.blogs.starnewsonline.com/11937/stephen-king-tv-series-under-the-dome-to-film-in-wilmington/|title=Stephen King TV series "Under the Dome" to film in Wilmington|work=Star News Online|last=Foss|first=Cassie|date=January 2, 2013|accessdate=January 3, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131007040913/http://wilmonfilm.blogs.starnewsonline.com/11937/stephen-king-tv-series-under-the-dome-to-film-in-wilmington/|archive-date=2013-10-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Radish|first=Christina|title=CBS' Nina Tassler Talks PERSON OF INTEREST, ELEMENTARY, Brian K. Vaughan’s UNDER THE DOME, HOW I MET YOUR MOTHER Season 9, and More|url=http://collider.com/nina-tassler-under-the-dome-person-of-interest-interview/223819/|publisher=Collider.com|accessdate=12 January 2013|date=12 January 2013|archive-date=2013-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130114074125/http://collider.com/nina-tassler-under-the-dome-person-of-interest-interview/223819/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://tvseriesfinale.com/tv-show/under-the-dome-tv-series-27122/|title=''Under the Dome'': Production Begins on New TV Series|work=TV Series Finale|date=February 28, 2013|accessdate=March 1, 2013}}</ref>
